3. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper deals with adversarial attacks and defenses, which are important topics in cybersecurity. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper involves the use of AI techniques to generate adversarial examples and to develop defense models. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image-based tasks and perturbations, which are relevant to multimedia applications.
